data.description: Beautiful 3 level home in friendly quite neighborhood. Enjoy relaxing views and sounds of a waterfall, fishpond & woods from your 3rd floor master or main floor balconies. Many new upgrades and extras. New refrigerator, main bathroom, master shower and flooring remodel. Exterior/interior paint, gazebo, large RV carport w/ power, gutters w/ leaf guard, fenced back yard, raised decks w/ awnings, finished garage, bonus heated game room and basement storage. Bonus-Storage basement, finish game room, garage cabinetry, outdoor kitchen w/ grill, smoker, bar & sink.
